# - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
# Colors:
#   red, orange, yellow, olive, green, teal, blue, violet, purple
#   pink, brown, grey, black.
# Buttons:
#   Add keyword 'basic' to have only border instead of a filled button.
#   Add keyword 'inverted' to display a button on a dark background.
